name: Hd Whitty Full Week!
description:
I have seen many people try to make a hd Whitty mod,But they were ether cancelled or they were still making it, so I decided to make one myself with some assets I found on other mods and twitter posts along with some custom dialouge,Credit to RingDedede for the ballistic assets and Kappa Nerd for the regular assets and remixed assets

Please Enjoy!
